A vintage 1950s-style illustration of a frustrated man in a retro living room holding a silver Palm PDA device, squinting at its tiny screen while peering enviously through a window at his neighbor who triumphantly holds up a sleek Nokia phone displaying a beautiful webpage. The scene uses warm sepia tones with pops of orange and teal, featuring mid-century modern furniture, a rotary phone on a side table, and dramatic venetian blind shadows casting across the room. The man's expression conveys longing and mild exasperation, his Palm device emitting faint wavy lines suggesting a weak or struggling connection.
